  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569660/extras/d5d35e3bb20647aeacbfe06c6b1ed521.avif?t=1772196942\" width=594 height=163 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569660/extras/0744119222ddadb3e5d4aac5cbe64150.poster.avif?t=1772196942\" width=594 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569660/extras/0744119222ddadb3e5d4aac5cbe64150.webm?t=1772196942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569660/extras/0744119222ddadb3e5d4aac5cbe64150.mp4?t=1772196942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Interballistic Symphony is a musical, fast-paced indie game all about speed and swift thinking.<br>Easy to learn, hard to master, interballistic features several levels set in galactic and cold, unforgiving environments.<br>Navigate through various obstacles and see how far you can make it.<br>Featuring a normal mode and a marathon mode for more casual gameplay and endless mode with highscore lists for competitive players.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569660/extras/ba0c5af413d1f569aebc7fc4963f579e.avif?t=1772196942\" width=594 height=163 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569660/extras/b531710f70c7a6f148abecd6a9cc2a25.webp?t=1772196942\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Several EDM soundtracks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569660/extras/b531710f70c7a6f148abecd6a9cc2a25.webp?t=1772196942\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Normal mode. Go from point A to point B.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569660/extras/b531710f70c7a6f148abecd6a9cc2a25.webp?t=1772196942\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Marathon mode. Multiple levels put together and speed being a more important factor than normal mode.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569660/extras/b531710f70c7a6f148abecd6a9cc2a25.webp?t=1772196942\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Endless mode. See how far you can make it, while the speed increase over time.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569660/extras/b531710f70c7a6f148abecd6a9cc2a25.webp?t=1772196942\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Powerups such as slowmotion, low gravity and score boosts to help you through tricky obstacles and reach new heights.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569660/extras/b531710f70c7a6f148abecd6a9cc2a25.webp?t=1772196942\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Set and save public highscores in endless mode.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2569660/extras/b531710f70c7a6f148abecd6a9cc2a25.webp?t=1772196942\" width=24 height=24 /></span> Discover collectibles, unlock a bunch of achievements and push your skills to the limit.",
